nswers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 3558, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 447415, "username": "git00ll", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/git00ll", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": null, "bio": null, "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/fe1424073ce8332fba272048de8f51a5?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/fe1424073ce8332fba272048de8f51a5?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/fe1424073ce8332fba272048de8f51a5?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1571285971, "last_modified": 1653977600}, "last_reply_by": "heygum97", "last_touched": 1663478359, "title": "如果你不想立刻去做媳妇让你做的事情时，大家是怎样处理的", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/880897", "created": 1663424157, "deleted": 0, "content": "生活相处中，可能需要做一些小事，比如\r\n\r\n倒一下洗脚水，脱下地，把衣服放洗衣机洗洗，洗衣机衣服晒一下，等等小事情。\r\n\r\n但是有时候你可能刚躺在沙发上玩会手机，范懒，想磨叽几十分钟后再做，可是媳妇让你立刻去，就会产生争执，大家是怎么处理这种场景的呢。\r\n\r\n\r\n小弟因为这种鸡毛蒜皮的事吵过几次了，想请教一下有经验的大哥。", "content_rendered": "<p>生活相处中，可能需要做一些小事，比如</p>\n<p>倒一下洗脚水，脱下地，把衣服放洗衣机洗洗，洗衣机衣服晒一下，等等小事情。</p>\n<p>但是有时候你可能刚躺在沙发上玩会手机，范懒，想磨叽几十分钟后再做，可是媳妇让你立刻去，就会产生争执，大家是怎么处理这种场景的呢。</p>\n<p>小弟因为这种鸡毛蒜皮的事吵过几次了，想请教一下有经验的大哥。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1663424200, "replies": 34, "id": 880897}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_large.png?m=1650095340", "name": "qna", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_normal.png?m=1650095340", "title": "问与答", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna", "topics": 190216, "footer": "", "header": "一个更好的世界需要你持续地提出好问题。", "title_alternative": "Questions and Answers", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340", "stars": 3558, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 12, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 215377, "username": "liyunlong0610", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/liyunlong0610", "website": null